data.description: Searching for peace and elegance?  Then you have found it!  Spacious 1.5 story home with over 5,400 finished sq.ft. sits on 8 acres of park-like land and backs up to Mt. St. Francis's walking trails and lake.  The main floor includes, updated custom kitchen w/quartz counters, tiled back splash, STAINLESS appliances and huge ISLAND w/cabinets galore.  Enjoy your living room w/GAS FIREPLACE or snuggle up in the family room in front of your beautiful STONE mantle w/WOOD STOVE.  The family room has hook-ups for wet-bar.  1st floor En-Suite has large walk thru closet, built-ins, HEATED TILED floors, large JETTED TUB and block-glass surround shower.  Second bedroom w/bath, den/office area.  Upstairs includes large bedroom w/BUILT-IN seating and large closet.  Spacious LOFT and another large room for craft, 2nd family room, media room, ect...
